description:
Bestjobs is the place where candidates and companies connect more easily.
With the help of Bestie and video interviews, the recruitment process becomes faster, more personal, and closer to you.
Bestie, your AI assistant in Bestjobs, recommends jobs that match you and helps you present yourself authentically through a simple and friendly video interview. You have access to thousands of jobs across Europe and can apply directly from the app, wherever you are.

For employers, Bestjobs means more efficient recruiting. Bestie provides recommendations for relevant candidates and video interviews recorded directly by interested talent. In addition, you can promote jobs, manage applications, and schedule interviews quickly, right from your phone.

Key features:
Chat with Bestie for job and candidate recommendations;
Create and send video interviews that make you stand out;
Apply to jobs that fit you or save them for later;
Receive instant notifications when a new job in your field appears.
